| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0531 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 496ed6ee-9cd9-5385-b6dc-f03e5d4ff344"
